title: Aviditi MDHD302020 Heavy-Duty Multi-Depth Corrugated Cardboard Box 30" L x 20" W x 20" H, Kraft, for Shipping, Packing and Moving (Pack of 10)
features: DIMENSIONS: Inside dimensions measure 30-inches (length) x 20-inches (width) x 20-inches (height). Carton capacity is approximately 6.944 cubic feet.

APPLICATIONS: Minimize the impact of UPS/FedEx dimensional weight pricing by eliminating empty space. To obtain the desired size, simply cut down to the pre-scored interval on the sides of the box. Great for packing, shipping, moving, and storage.

TOP QUALITY: Multi-Depth style cartons offer the benefits of having many box sizes in inventory without using up valuable storage space. Boxes are easy to assemble, fold together in seconds and are proudly made in the United States.

MATERIAL & STRENGTH: Heavy-Duty Multi-Depth Boxes are manufactured from 275#/ECT-44 singlewall, c-flute kraft corrugated. Estimated weight capacity is 95 lbs. (This is only a guide, weight must be distributed evenly).

PACKAGING: Package includes 10 boxes per bundle and ship flat to save on storage, space and shipping. Heavy-Duty construction and multi-depth style provide greater protection, stacking strength and flexibility. Boxes are reusable and recyclable.
